@startuml audio_ducking_from_alert_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Audio Ducking From Alert Signal Flow\n(CGW -> IVI -> CLU / AMP)

participant "CGW\neffective alert gate" as CGW #FFF4CC
participant "IVI\nwarning render + focus owner" as IVI #E8F0FE
participant "CLU\ncluster/media mirror" as CLU #E8F0FE
participant "AMP\naudio ducking output" as AMP #FFE6E6

== Effective Alert Intake ==

activate CGW
CGW -> IVI : CoreState::selectedAlertEffectiveLevel / Type
CGW -> IVI : Core::timeoutClear
note right of CGW
Representative source
- selectedAlertEffectiveLevel
- selectedAlertEffectiveType
- timeoutClear
end note
deactivate CGW

== IVI HMI / Audio Focus Publish ==

activate IVI
CGW -> IVI : effective alert seams
IVI -> IVI : deriveWarningTextCode()
IVI -> IVI : compatBeepEmergency / compatBeepIC / compatBeepSpeed
IVI -> IVI : UiRender::warningBeepState
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmHmiPopupStateMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmMediaStateMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmAudioFocusMsg
IVI -> AMP : frmMediaStateMsg
IVI -> AMP : frmAudioFocusMsg
note right of IVI
Representative outputs
- frmAudioFocusMsg
- frmMediaStateMsg
- frmClusterWarningMsg
- UiRender::warningBeepState
end note
deactivate IVI

== Cluster Mirror ==

activate CLU
IVI -> CLU : frmAudioFocusMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmMediaStateMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg
CLU -> CLU : CoreState::audioFocusOwner
CLU -> CLU : CoreState::audioDuckingLvl
deactivate CLU

== AMP Ducking ==

activate AMP
IVI -> AMP : frmMediaStateMsg
IVI -> AMP : frmAudioFocusMsg
AMP -> AMP : traceAmpInputHealth()
AMP -> AMP : if input lease valid,\napply audioFocusOwner / audioDuckingLvl
AMP -> AMP : if focus input expired,\nclear focus owner and ducking
note right of AMP
Representative outputs
- ampDucking
- audio focus owner
- ducking level
end note
deactivate AMP

note over CGW, AMP
Representative runtime chain
1. CGW publishes effective alert state
2. IVI derives warning text / beep and audio focus
3. IVI sends audio focus + media state to CLU and AMP
4. AMP applies ducking while CLU mirrors focus state
end note

@enduml
